{
  "texts": [
    "Once having analyzed what can be done with the combination of iVR and wearable biosensors, further testing needs to be conducted to better understand the full range of iVR and wearable biosensor combinations.",
    "To do so, experiments should be conducted with a sufficiently large enough sample to reach conclusive results.",
    "In such experiences, a minimum of 40 participants is expected to extract conclusive results and to study additional aspects in the post-assessments, which will in the near future lead to improved experiences.",
    "In future research, network and cluster classifications will be conducted, to explore correlations between the various characteristics of the experiences and the applications that may be presented in each paper."
  ]
}